WEBVTT

00:00:01.747 --> 00:00:03.234
This is Henry,

00:00:03.258 --> 00:00:05.064
a cute boy,

00:00:05.088 --> 00:00:07.226
and when Henry was three,

00:00:07.250 --> 00:00:12.185
his mom found him having
some febrile seizures.

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:18.040
Febrile seizures are seizures that occur
when you also have a fever,

00:00:18.064 --> 00:00:19.962
and the doctor said,

00:00:19.986 --> 00:00:22.728
"Don't worry too much.
Kids usually outgrow these."

00:00:23.506 --> 00:00:27.487
When he was four,
he had a convulsive seizure,

00:00:27.511 --> 00:00:30.773
the kind that you lose
consciousness and shake --